data.description: You must see this beautiful 2BR/1.75BA home on a corner lot located in the amazing 55+ community of Sun City.   Enter your new home to a very spacious living room with elegant laminate wood flooring and a formal dining area with plenty of natural light.   This extremely popular Annapolis model includes an open kitchen/great room design featuring extra cabinets, pull-out shelves, under cabinet lighting, Corian counters, and an informal dining area which opens to the back patio.  Both bedrooms are nice sized and include walk-in closets.  Additional features include an exceptionally large inside laundry which doubles as an office/den.  Newer Heat Pump and Solar on home reduces electric bills.   Relax outside under an extended covered patio, complete with Saltillo tile, ceiling fans, an outdoor sink with cupboards, and plenty of shaded sitting areas to enjoy your private backyard retreat.  This is the one.  To show is to sell.
